{"tid":1744132,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[江湖傳聞]她知道，哭是沒有用的。","createTime":"2019-11-21T14:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T14:50:47.000Z","uid":7131,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d3b3ddf06ebd321de27b56945f7f99680153becf","tid":1744132,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:20:55.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊為父還債，所以61歲出道，開始了自己的僭建生涯。若驊僭建第一間屋《海詩別墅》時，他和300多人打打殺殺，因為太過投入，他不小心打到了廢鋼鐵，左手立即脫臼，淚如泉湧。<br />\n<br />\n樂陶立刻喊停，要送她去醫院。她知道，這一去醫院，勢必要換人，那他的「官途」也許從此就斷了。於是，61歲的他對林鄭說：「找來300多人不容易，耽誤一天就是好多錢，我能堅持。」於是，他將酒精直接倒在傷口上，再將膠袋包著手，穿上貼身樽領繼續僭建。換了四個膠袋，倒出四袋血，樓起完時，她幾乎暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n送到醫院，醫生說，再遲來一點，人就玩完了，而且，極有可能會截肢。在給他駁臼之前，醫生讓他簽生死狀。 在醫生給他駁臼時，鄭若驊就那麼看著，不喊、不叫、不哭，沒有打麻醉針，就那樣一下一下地駁返。一個61歲的美魔女，知道自己面對的是怎樣的人生。她知道，哭是沒有用的。<br />\n<br />\n最後一針，若驊對醫生說：「我來駁！」醫生看著她，她居然笑了︰「沒有嘗試過的人生，我都想嘗試一下。」<br />\n<br />\n這句話多麼豪邁，在場的人震驚了。因為醫生說，如果熬不過去，她也只有四天的生命了，所以，她願意嘗試生命中不曾嘗試的痛，她要自己駁返左手。<br />\n<br />\n從給自己駁手那一天開始，她知道，所有的明天全要靠自己。後來，她一直努力，不停地僭建，終於得到第三十屆DMM.R18成人獎最優秀新人獎。"},{"pid":"ac3df0a2dd54f55075a7930da5ebd62ed84d3d50","tid":1744132,"uid":314136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"巨乳六十路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3f1e213ca1deb7dce438f7558065084d5cd0d6","tid":1744132,"uid":258144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"有關內容完全捏造 非常無聊"},{"pid":"087c9ac0eacb9c00ffd3f536d07b24615b25cf22","tid":1744132,"uid":16109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"0/10<br />\n<br />\n假咗啲，但繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321767a05122453f121836aa45e3b68ca2064ce3","tid":1744132,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:23:50.000Z","msg":"DMM.R18<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ace8a2ca48bfba9b2fbb9455df863b6237f4f96","tid":1744132,"uid":7131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd337b3f81dbc744274ad7c739c45de9cccdfbd1","tid":1744132,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"喂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa9ffe4cc21242ab30b1aa0c35c603993d94be0","tid":1744132,"uid":268386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"律政司幾時回應"},{"pid":"fe0886073e74e4005bcb630fc4763f1c9faf4d11","tid":1744132,"uid":38548,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"玩還玩<br />\n小心政府藉機打擊連登公信力"},{"pid":"b0f9a3ef699726bcfa8d7ca4edbcd72da791323e","tid":1744132,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe0886073e74e4005bcb630fc4763f1c9faf4d11","tid":1744132,"uid":38548,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"玩還玩<br />\n小心政府藉機打擊連登公信力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"exact7ly"},{"pid":"6bd339b01838025d25af3a499f197190c1e8cd14","tid":1744132,"uid":20362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fe0886073e74e4005bcb630fc4763f1c9faf4d11","tid":1744132,"uid":38548,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"玩還玩<br />\n小心政府藉機打擊連登公信力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n有咩公信力可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f543508356cd74796bb47e2daf1c7cdfe1c01a5","tid":1744132,"uid":7131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bd339b01838025d25af3a499f197190c1e8cd14","tid":174